          "Your relationship to these people is described. This may mean they do not know you."
        ],
        [
          "Wade Carlson III",
          "The Gangrel are vicious killers, which means they are excellent first subjects for your further studies into the mysteries of Golconda."
        ],
        [
          "Isha Parikh",
          "Golconda means Lore, and Isha is a known Loremaster in Tremere. Perhaps she can help you uncover truths about Golconda your books kept hidden."
        ],
        [
          "Eayan Aleasif",
          "You know Golconda means transformation, and no one has been transformed more than a Gargoyle! Seek to understand his condition."
        ],
        [],
        [
          "Starting Goals",
          "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        ],
        [
          "Discover more about Golconda, what it means and how to find it. Golconda isn't a subject believed by most, so be careful with whom you speak about it."
        ],
        [
          "Your urge to kill is in direct contradiction of your wishing to find Golconda. Malkav's curse can never be relieved, but perhaps it can be changed? Find a way to either indulge your Derangement in a way which does not cost you Humanity, or shift its focus, if you can."
        ],
        [
          "You've killed a lot of Brujah. None of them were Camarilla, so they can't get you for breaking Right of Destruction But the clan, as a result, dislikes you. Find a way to fix that."
        ],
